Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really gonna track them\Ndown using research papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be hard to even run clinical\Ntrials for an artificial heart like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be a fiasco if you\Ndid a transplant and it failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alan Institute gave them an opportunity\Nto unlawfully carry out experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Lycoris don't have family\Nregisters, so they're a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some catalyst that\Nled to Alan finding that researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are just... naked men, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's time\Nwe put an end to it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LycoReco's going to close up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The brave choice we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Its future is being illuminated♫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If we clash our selfish emotions\Nwe can't see it (yet)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫To catch up on the distance\Nwe fled from (see) let's go on a journey♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Even if we can't see the farthest lands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We just burn our lives\Nto keep living in the present♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Proof of the existence we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We kept our voices trembling\Nwhile we brandished it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫No need for regret, we go\Nhand in hand (even the dark past)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We accept it and move forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Instead of choosing an answer shown to us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We're aspiring a new dream (always)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Let's walk along the radiant road♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(#10 Repay evil with evil)\NI'd feel bad making you waste time on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this café needs to be\Na fun place until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with that, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the original plan, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lasted a lot longer than we thought.\NIsn't that right, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone needs to learn from Takina\Nand find their own path again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Mizuki, where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go meet up with the hottie in\NVancouver I met on a matchmaking site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's jacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! And you, Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is in danger in this\Ncountry without you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you've got DA after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave from this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should go to Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again with the board games?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The birthplace of it all!\NThey even have big contests there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you come as well.\NI can whip up a passport for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Sensei would be lonely,\Nso no one can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell Takina to visit someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with the arms deal in April,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the subway attack,\NLycoris killings, police station attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mastermind behind all of these\Nplots is this man named Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warmonger who's traveled\Nall over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was confirmed to be in this\Ncountry 10 years ago as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radio tower incident\NI'm sure you all know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believed everyone had been executed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's had a First uniform\Nsince she was that young?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majima's taken on jobs from mafia\Nboth domestic and abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his target is the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've apprehended one of his clients\Nand identified Majima's hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll strike with all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him and kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her heart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good idea now\Nof your relationship with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not innocent here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'd come as a real letdown if she\Nknew what her hero Yoshi-san was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to that, my life ended up\Nbeing spared in the radio tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I warned you, Alan Institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I betrayed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it against Alan rules to take\Naction just because your plans went awry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my error that led to her\Nstraying from her path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just carrying out my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you kill me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an exemplary Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were the 1,000 guns enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you patronize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as her, you know.\NLiving the way I see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I might see it fit to\Nblow your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's to fulfill Alan's ideals,\NI'm more than prepared to offer my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're creeping me out, goddamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lot are the same as DA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lurking in the shadows and manipulating\Nthe world for your self-centered justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you after DA, Alan Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your headquarters? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to the airport this time\Nwithout being stuffed in that suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NThat pout's ruining your cute face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care too, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave Chisato in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too hard on him, Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting on in years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start cleaning up, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could we do? It's what Chisato wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say a single word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still Takina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Majima's client?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His target is the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who supplied him the guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in having a thousand guns\Nwithout the soldiers to use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Yoshimatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshimatsu? Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think my fellow men were\Nmurdered by kids like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was discharged from here once\Nfor being too trigger-happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turns out life outside\Nwasn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn't mind if it happened ag...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any Yoshimatsu! I swear I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alan! He called himself Alan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alan Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea! That's all I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Yoshimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Enkuboku is finally completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the completion ceremony\Ntomorrow looms closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,preparations around the site\Nare steadily progressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was watching that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be cleaning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Riki! He sure was cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei. What will you do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go meet a realtor\Ntomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean like taking on a job\Npart-time to continue the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna be out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to say my proper goodbyes\Nto the café as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw right through me, huh, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I make us some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo green. Delta green. Charlie green.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha-1, all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look at this crowd!\NWhat is this, a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your teacher chaperone's with you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one in charge of\Nhaving you killed, Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I don't need to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Lycoris head honcho, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's that, too.\NMy men need to eat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more than that, I took\Nthe job because it interested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interested? In what, aiding the mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In seeing what you villains pretending\Nto be on the side of justice were like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only villains here are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The law is the modern-day measure of\Nwhat's right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you people operate under the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have operated before the law ever existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have preserved this nation's order\Nand morals across political regimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and find the broadcast location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Across regimes? Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of telling you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a result, we've protected\Nthis nation's interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Machiavellianism? How old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would the public think if they\Nknew all this has gone unpunished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unnecessary concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True peace only exists in a world where\Nthe very presence of evil is unfelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too will vanish and leave\Nno trace in anyone's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By manipulating information as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the absence of harsh reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it possible that people will forget\Nthe very meaning of peace itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that it's something you secure for\Nyourself, not something you're given.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clever one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose villains can't handle\Nthe truth of their own evil ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this to try and help you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scales of right and wrong, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which way they tip, they\Nshouldn't be controlled by groups like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The balance must be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's your reason for\Ntargeting the Enkuboku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that much already,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be unbalanced if I\Ndidn't destroy them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the guns from that arms dealer,\Nit'll end the same as 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so? Think she'll show up\Nagain to save your skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Lycoris head honcho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the dark-haired one. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ended up back here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yoshimatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you want to know\Nabout Yoshi-san as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular fellow, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in you.\NTell me where Yoshimatsu is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take it easy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! We're at our limit!\NCut the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee there should still be warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The connection's been severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to capture the last host!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The latest access point is\Nin Ota City, Kamata district!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's all this? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are personal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to draw my manga now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any other cafés\Nthat are as nice and quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, make sure you guys\Ncome back... Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, owner, isn't this a bit too sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider closing this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still... kinda heartwarming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security Lycoris all in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the Enkuboku\Ncompletion ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take the mic, Governor Onuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this box been sitting here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we lock up?\NWe might get more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. It's not a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a special occasion. Although it's a bit\Nearly for your coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got a good picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!\NI'm asking you what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you look wonderful, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown into a fine young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done a single thing\Nfor you to thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who gave me my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you taught me how to shoot a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this café, and meeting Takina as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most importantly, you're the one who\Nfound Yoshi-san for my sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You should send Yoshi-san\Nthat picture you just took!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No harm i...\N- That's not the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Sensei? No need to yell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I need to\Ntell you about Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've located Majima's vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redirecting northwards,\Nclear of the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blocking off all other routes\Nto the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If his aim is to destroy it,\Nhe'll be aiming for these spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlie in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target has bypassed the projected point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means we've cornered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Control Room)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you, my hacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared this backdoor all for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I let Shinji operate on you\Nfor my own interests as commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least that was the case at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just needs to live for\Nas long as she's a Lycoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'll take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I want you to promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise her to be the world's greatest hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're lying. Yoshi-san said he\Nwas a savior who helped people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You grew to idolize Shinji more and more,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became your source of power to\Nlive a life that could end at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So brilliant... yet empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish I had told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shinji would come save you\Nagain if you kept killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me, Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me make the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had told me, I probably\Nwould have given in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have probably carried out\Nmy work as a Lycoris, reluctantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'd blame you or Yoshi-san\Nfor all of my pain and hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate that! Nope, that'd suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The work I did, starting this café...\NI decided all that for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gratitude I feel towards you and\NYoshi-san for letting me do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed a bit\Nafter hearing what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are my dads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Sensei - Me - Savior)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that makes me the happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I turn out? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud you're my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, to conclude the Enkuboku\Ncompletion ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will transmit a broadcast signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time as the countdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the system inside the Enkuboku\Nwill automatically transmit a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now please join me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, ignorant masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at, Majima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other nations are embroiled\Nin war and terrorist attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet this country is as peaceful as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because its citizens are so well behaved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the Japanese are so amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the worthless take pride in\Nbeing pigeonholed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is rife with terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that all of it has been suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forced into a peace\Ntainted by lies and hyperbole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All its blemishes covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those in this country who\Ncling to such a tainted idea of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've scattered guns just like\Nthese across the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the thousand guns were for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not approach any civilians\Nwho possess guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fire under any circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His true goal is to expose\Nthe existence of Lycoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got it wrong, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now fire to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And defend yourselves against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you do with those is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real world free of lies aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Please stand by)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've shut off the signal from the Enkuboku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, a call from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusunoki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still control\Ninformation using Radiata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ensure that the existence of\Nthe Lycoris remains a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your existence was hinted at\Nin a nationwide broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this not a failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you not deploy Chisato Nishikigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this not exactly the situation\Nyou keep her around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the operation planning to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusunoki-kun, could it be that\Nyou think too little of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy Chisato Nishikigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only option left to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A state of emergency has been declared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorists have taken over the Enkuboku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- and have hijacked the signal.\N- What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is a man in his thirties...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusunoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me speak to Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato's not available to talk right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to headquarters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet up, and you'll head to\Nthe Enkuboku to take down Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get anywhere near the Enkuboku and he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is gonna blow in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation calls for a Lycoris like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great number of lives are on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have a Lycoris like you showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's life is on the line here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kusunoki, I'll call back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. Don't make any rash moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be keeping a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean I can\Njust leave him to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, Shinji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to hear what Yoshi-san\Nhas to say in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a chance to get rid of\Nall the ammo in the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to take all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina and Fuki will keep the Enkuboku safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you, those two are\Nmy finest students.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The manga you brought me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The flower you gave me\Nthat I don't know the name of♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You're not here yet today?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫I am aware of an emotion never felt before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:23:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Tracing along a picture decorating\Nthe window, I travel through space alone♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫That should have been enough♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If I were to grab your hand♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫This town that knows not of solitude♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Becomes one that I can\Nnever return to ever again♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You reached your hand out to me,\Nand a shadow is born from the light♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.47,0:23:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Sing for me to listen\Nthe continuation of this story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Take me to a star that I've never seen before♫
